Parmesan Carrot Fries Recipe
http://dailyburn.com/life/recipes/healthy-carrot-fries-recipe/
Serves 4 
Prep Time: 10 minutes
Cook Time: 15 minutes

1 pound fresh carrots
2 teaspoons olive oil
1/2 teaspoon flaky sea salt
Cracked black pepper, to taste
2 tablespoons fresh basil, chopped
2-3 tablespoons freshly grated Parmesan

Preheat oven to 450 F.
Peel carrots and cut into thin matchstick slices.
In a medium bowl, toss slices in olive oil, salt and pepper.
Spread out carrots on a baking sheet and bake for 12 to 15 minutes or until
the carrots are browned slightly.
Remove from the oven and sprinkle with fresh basil and Parmesan cheese
before serving.
